name: $resourceType
desc: Returns the FHIR type name for this instance

name: $identifier
desc: Returns: Unique identifier used to reference the account.  May or may not be intended for human use (e.g. credit card number).

name: $addidentifier
desc: Unique identifier used to reference the account.  May or may not be intended for human use (e.g. credit card number).

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Unique identifier used to reference the account.  May or may not be intended for human use (e.g. credit card number).

name: $status
desc: Returns: Indicates whether the account is presently used/usable or not.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Indicates whether the account is presently used/usable or not.

name: $::type
desc: Returns: Categorizes the account for reporting and searching purposes.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Categorizes the account for reporting and searching purposes.

name: $::name
desc: Returns: Name used for the account when displaying it to humans in reports, etc.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Name used for the account when displaying it to humans in reports, etc.

name: $subject
desc: Returns: Identifies the patient, device, practitioner, location or other object the account is associated with.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Identifies the patient, device, practitioner, location or other object the account is associated with.

name: $period
desc: Returns: Identifies the period of time the account applies to; e.g. accounts created per fiscal year, quarter, etc.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Identifies the period of time the account applies to; e.g. accounts created per fiscal year, quarter, etc.

name: $active
desc:
Returns: Indicates the period of time over which the account is allowed to have transactions posted to it.
This period may be different to the coveragePeriod which is the duration of time that services may occur.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc:
Indicates the period of time over which the account is allowed to have transactions posted to it.
This period may be different to the coveragePeriod which is the duration of time that services may occur.

name: $balance
desc: Returns: Represents the sum of all credits less all debits associated with the account.  Might be positive, zero or negative.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Represents the sum of all credits less all debits associated with the account.  Might be positive, zero or negative.

name: $coverage
desc: Returns: The party(s) that are responsible for covering the payment of this account, and what order should they be applied to the account.

name: $addcoverage
desc: The party(s) that are responsible for covering the payment of this account, and what order should they be applied to the account.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: The party(s) that are responsible for covering the payment of this account, and what order should they be applied to the account.

name: $owner
desc: Returns: Indicates the organization, department, etc. with responsibility for the account.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Indicates the organization, department, etc. with responsibility for the account.

name: $description
desc: Returns: Provides additional information about what the account tracks and how it is used.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Provides additional information about what the account tracks and how it is used.

name: $guarantor
desc: Returns: Parties financially responsible for the account.

name: $addguarantor
desc: Parties financially responsible for the account.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Parties financially responsible for the account.
